HEADWORD: Profulgent
<hw>Pro*ful"gent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>pro-</ets> + L. <ets>fulgere</ets> to shine.]</ety> <def>Shining
forth; brilliant; effulgent.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Profulgent</xex> in preciousness.⟦rdquo⟧
